About Anthropic
Anthropic’s mission is to create reliable, interpretable, and steerable AI systems. We want AI to be safe and beneficial for our users and for society as a whole. Our team is a quickly growing group of committed researchers, engineers, policy experts, and business leaders working together to build beneficial AI systems.

About the role:
Anthropic is pioneering safe and reliable AI assistants. As we continue to advance industry-leading language models, we aim to empower users worldwide to build trustworthy and transformative generative AI applications.

We are seeking exceptional Technical Partner Enablement Leads to drive technical education and enablement for our strategic cloud and technology partners. In this highly technical role, you will create and deliver technical content and training that empowers partners to build cutting-edge solutions with Claude. Working closely with our partnerships team, you will serve as a technical expert who can engage deeply with partner engineering teams, solutions architects, and technical leaders.

Your mission will be to lead high-impact technical events and create compelling content that showcases Claude's advanced capabilities to developers. Through a combination of conference keynotes, technical hackathons, developer podcasts, and hands-on workshops, you'll showcase Claude's advanced capabilities and help technical audiences push the boundaries of what's possible with frontier AI models.

This role offers the opportunity to shape how leading technology companies understand and implement Claude's capabilities. Your work will directly influence how partners build with and teach others about Claude.

About Anthropic 

Anthropic is an AI safety and research company that's working to build reliable, interpretable, and steerable AI systems. We want AI to be safe and beneficial for our customers and for society as a whole. Our interdisciplinary team has experience across ML, physics, policy, business and product.

